You may view the source code in this repository for evaluation and collaboration within the GKGuard project context. You may not copy, redistribute, sublicense, sell, host as a competing service, or use this code in another product without prior written permission from the repository owner.

Third-party dependencies, frameworks, tools, and models keep their own licenses. Review their license terms before redistribution, production deployment, or packaging.

Sensitive operational data must not be committed to this repository. This includes real campus videos, query images, extracted frames, face crops, SQLite runtime databases, model caches, secrets, server passwords, private keys, `.env` files, and personally identifiable information.

For permission requests, contact the repository owner through GitHub.
